<chapter condition="TITLE=FSCM Services" id="FS_Main" role="TOPIC">
  <title>SCF Services</title>

  <para role="TEXT">The SCF Services menu on the toolbar, provides facilities
  to manage purchase orders, invoices and credit notes, through the
  <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>.</para>

  <note>
    <para role="TEXT">The availability of the SCF Services menu and its
    functions is dependent on the permissions assigned to the user. Only those
    functions the user is authorised to use, will be displayed.</para>
  </note>

  <para role="TEXT">This menu provides a number of modules, as follows:</para>

  <para role="TEXT"><variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Invoice</guimenuitem></term>

        <listitem>
          <para role="TEXT">Load and process invoices for Sellers</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Invoice
        Payable</guimenuitem></term>

        <listitem>
          <para role="TEXT">Load, process and pay invoices from Buyers</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Credit Note -
        Seller</guimenuitem></term>

        <listitem>
          <para role="TEXT">Load and process for Credit Note seller</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Credit Note - Buyer
        </guimenuitem></term>

        <listitem>
          <para role="TEXT">Load and process for Credit Note buyer</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist></para>

